<sect1 id="dir_52936351db34d2a1eebd36b673ba9c6c_1autotoc_md282">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::scheduling</title><para>Spawn scheduling and plan management.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_52936351db34d2a1eebd36b673ba9c6c_1autotoc_md283">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides the scheduling layer for the spawn system. The SpawnScheduler evaluates spawn rules and produces ScheduledSpawnPlan instances that are then processed by the command pipeline.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_52936351db34d2a1eebd36b673ba9c6c_1autotoc_md284">
